Company Overview of H. J. Umbaugh and Associates, Certified Public Accountants, LLP



Snapshot People




Company Overview
H. J. Umbaugh and Associates, Certified Public Accountants, LLP provides accounting and financial advisory services. The company offers audit preparation, bond issuance, financial reporting, and tax revenue analysis and management. It also provides project inception and completion assistance, financial analysis, and long-term planning to local governments, utilities, schools, and libraries. H. J. Umbaugh and Associates, Certified Public Accountants, LLP is based in Indianapolis, Indiana.


8365 Keystone CrossingSuite 300Indianapolis, IN 46240United States



Phone: 317-465-1500

Fax: 317-465-1550

www.umbaugh.com







