H. J. Umbaugh and Associates, Certified Public Accountants, LLP Key Developments

Umbaugh Names Mark A. Miller as Director for its Columbus Office
May 5 16
Umbaugh has named former PNC Capital Markets managing director and supervisory principal Mark A. Miller to the new position for Umbaugh's Columbus, Ohio office. Miller has been a public finance professional for more than 25 years serving state treasurers, state agencies, counties, cities, colleges and universities, school districts, convention centers and airports. Over the years, Miller has managed bond financings for many of Ohio's issuers and for issuers in Indiana, Michigan, Pennsylvania, North Carolina and Kentucky.


